{"tid":955292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"福建男脅持巴士撞人群滿地傷者 至少5死21傷","createTime":"2018-12-25T09:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T11:49:17.000Z","uid":41404,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"71d0e344f28b9faf8ed96cf89188489ac4aa086e","tid":955292,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T09:34:05.000Z","msg":"今日福建省龍岩市一名男子，據悉因不滿政府遷拆，脅持一架巴士並胡亂撞向街道途人，造成至少5死21傷，死者包括一名警員。福建省龍岩市公安局指出，目前疑兇已被捕。<br />\n<br />\n當地黨委、政府正在全力救助傷者，疑兇在事發後在現場被捕，案件正在調查中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181225/59069403\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181225%2F59069403&d=%2Bx%2FO5aMVOz%2Fb6Hk2i1FBc9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=3e1b7383\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181225%2F59069403&h=86bfc384\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181225/59069403</a>"},{"pid":"8e942292945b34852c309ad6b5fc6a801b0300a9","tid":955292,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T11:12:47.000Z","msg":"又贏<br />\n<br />\n減少人口負擔<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a4b3c393c827173976b1e365aabff7164f4500","tid":955292,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T11:25:08.000Z","msg":"我估最終死亡人數為35人"},{"pid":"966e346a76790bd4b31b5137f689f6d60a894597","tid":955292,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T11:25:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37454f0bb10ee5a841bcbbb8fd45f16723eda209","tid":955292,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T11:45:06.000Z","msg":"<img 